NB. =========================================================
NB. get active positions (that can move to empty)
getmoves=: 3 : 0
EMPTY=: {. ALLPOS -. {:"1 POS
msk=. +/"1 EMPTY = MOVEPOS
pot=. (msk # MOVECLR) ,. (msk # MOVEPOS) -."1 EMPTY
ACTIVE=: EMPTY -.~ , }."1 pot intersect POS
)

NB. =========================================================
NB. test rects for hit
NB. form: centers inrects pos
NB. returns hit index, or _1 if none
inrect=: 4 : 0
index1 *./"1 RAD >: | x -"1 y
)

