NB. move

NB. =========================================================
NB. movemark v move the marked coin
movemark=: 3 : 0
pos=. {.y
mov=. sort pos,.EMPTY
clr=. MOVECLR {~ MOVEPOS i. mov
DONE=: (clr=0) *. EMPTY = ENDPOS
POS=: (clr,EMPTY), POS -. clr,pos
LASTEMPTY=: EMPTY
COUNT=: BUFNDX=: >: BUFNDX
BUFFER=: (BUFNDX {. BUFFER), <POS
paint''
if. DONE do.
  info 'Finished.'
end.
)


